### Update an employee
PUT {{task_manager_backend_HostAddress}}/api/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "designation": "Principal Software Engineer",
  "salary": 120000,
  "status": "active"
}

### Delete an employee
DELETE {{task_manager_backend_HostAddress}}/api/employees/1

### Get employees by department
GET {{task_manager_backend_HostAddress}}/api/employees/department/Engineering
Accept: application/json

### Get employees by status
GET {{task_manager_backend_HostAddress}}/api/employees/status/active
Accept: application/json

### Get employees by location
GET {{task_manager_backend_HostAddress}}/api/employees/location/Bangalore
Accept: application/json

### Get employees by manager
GET {{task_manager_backend_HostAddress}}/api/employees/manager/5
Accept: application/json

